  "title": "Marketing",
  "description": "<p><strong>Benefit</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>OFFICE HOUR (8:30 AM TO 6:00 PM)– MONDAY TO FRIDAY</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>NEARBY MATTAR MRT &amp; ALJUNIED MRT STATION</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>WORK-LIFE BALANCE AND FRIENDLY ENVIRONMENT</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>With close to 3 decades of experience in the flooring industry, the company has built a reputation for its service and knowledge.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>We are looking for a Digital Marketing Executive focusing on social media and content writing. Working with the marketing team, you will be instrumental in building a digital presence and shaping our brand image.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Your day-to-day responsibilities include:</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>·       Handling our social media accounts, including</p>\n<p>(Instagram | TikTok | YouTube | Google Business Account)</p>\n<p>·       Blog/article writing</p>\n<p>·       Be aware of relevant social media trends</p>\n<p>·       Ensuring consistent branding in all social media platforms</p>\n<p>·       Assist in other marketing tasks when needed</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Requirements:</strong></em></p>\n<p>·       Diploma in Business Development, Marketing, or any other related field</p>\n<p>·       Ability to work independently.</p>\n<p>·       Good knowledge of SEO with a focus on keyword research</p>\n<p>·       Familiar with various digital marketing tools such as SEO tools, social listening tools.</p>\n<p>·       Knowledge of how different social media platform works and be able to propose the kind of content needed.</p>\n<p>·       Minimal Knowledge in Canva and Video Editing (preferred)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
