    "description": "<p>Company Overview</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Vix Marketing was incorporated in 1999 with the purpose of ensuring quality flooring and superior after sales services reach the recreational facilities. Our aim is to be a leader in the flooring industry in Singapore. In order to provide better service to our clients, Vix Marketing has been constantly expanding the range of her service. Besides specializing in the supply, installation we have also diversified into recreational products. Constantly working with tried and tested principles of service and quality, we strive in every possible way to support our clients and make them happy and successful</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
